{"title":"遥望","authors":["梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":3,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在革命博物馆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥望人民大会堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要说远，也不远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要说长，也很长："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长征二万五千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不及这路程一半强；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草鞋一双接一双，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能把那征途来比量！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在人民大会堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝望革命博物馆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说它长，也很长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说它远，也不远："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民英雄纪念碑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在中间路变短；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一面红旗对国徽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几十年星光血中闪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在英雄纪念碑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"环望四方都光辉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年烈士挖战壕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是奠基把石垒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年烈士杀敌回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦里早把蓝图绘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绘就远景如近景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"景色更比今天美！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}